Package twodtree

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ListOfCrimes
    This class maintains a singly linked list of SingleNode objects which are found in the range of the rectangle.
    Neighbor
    This class contains the detail of the neighbor Node with distance and point details.
    Node
    This class contains a Node which represents a node in 2d tree with a String[] data and right and left subtree
    Queue
    This class is a linked list implementation of the queue with a front and rear pointer.
    SingleNode
    The class implements an object with data as Node.
    Stack
    This class implements a stack using a linked list of SingleNode object with only a front pointer
    TwoDTree
    This class implements the creation, different traversals, range search and nearest neighbor of a 2-D tree.
    TwoDTreeDriver
    This class contains the main method.
